<p>The advanced search form can be accessed from the header menu of any admin page. The search field in the header menu also provides access to the advanced search functionality.</p>

<p><%= cdn_image "titleleaf-advanced-search-link.png", alt: "Advanced search link" %></p>

<p>If you click the "Advanced Search" link in the header menu, you will be presented with the advanced search form. Enter the search criteria into this form.</p>

<p><%= cdn_image "titleleaf-advanced-search-form.png", alt: "Advanced search form" %></p>

<p>Click the "Search" button at the bottom of the form to obtain the search results. This is the same page that you'll be presented if you use the search field in the header menu.</p>

<p><%= cdn_image "titleleaf-search-results.png", alt: "Search results" %></p>

<p>To fine-tune your search results, adjust the search filters in the right sidebar as desired, then click the "Perform" button.</p>

<p><%= cdn_image "titleleaf-search-results-filtered.png", alt: "Search results, refined" %></p>

<p>Individual products can be omitted from the search results by clicking the "Omit" icon in the respective product row.</p>

<p><%= cdn_image "titleleaf-search-results-omit.png", alt: "Omit search results" %></p>

<p>At any point, your search results can be exported using the respective form at the bottom of the right sidebar.</p>
